name: SpaceboyJJ
description:
This game was developed in school, by two students with the free to use engine Godot, with help from our teacher Hunter99. Yes, we aren't professionals... but we did have fun making the game, in wich Jörgen an astronaut from earth, travels through realities, with his biggest enemy: Karl the purple alien. We also did all of the assets ourselfs. :)

It's probably impossible, but please do not steal our game to make money :)
